    "description": "You'll be amping up your veggie burger game by making your own sweetcorn patties, packed full of flavours like basil, garlic and tahini for this delicious veggie winner. You'll also make a sun-dried tomato mayo to spread onto fluffy brioche buns. Serve the cheese-topped burgers up alongside crispy chips. Delicious!",
